# (R308), Standard ML stdlib GetOpt (R309),
# Fortran M_CLI2 (R310), Guile (ice-9 getopt-
# long) (R311), Free Pascal 1 FCL TCustom
# Application (R312), Idris 2 System.GetOpts
# (R313), Mercury stdlib getopt_io (R314),
# Eiffel Gobo AP_PARSER (R315), C++ 2 boost::
# program_options (R316), Forth/Gforth `next-
# arg` (R317), Clojure 2 org.clojure/tools.cli
